Package: gbifrules
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to GBIF Rule-Based Annotations Store
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John Waller <jwaller@gbif.org>
Maintainer: John Waller <jwaller@gbif.org>
Description: Facilitates interaction with the GBIF
  (Global Biodiversity Information Facility) rule-based annotation store. The
  package allows users to access, retrieve, and manage data utilizing the
  annotation store's data for analysis. Accesses the GBIF Occurrence 
  Annotation API <https://api.gbif.org/v1/occurrence/annotation>.
URL: https://github.com/gbif/occurrence-annotation
BugReports: https://github.com/gbif/occurrence-annotation/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
  tibble,
  tidyr,
  dplyr,
  purrr,
  httr2,
  sf,
  jsonlite,
  cli
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr,
    pkgdown,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    rgbif
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
License: Apache License (>= 2)
